类 SubscriberExceptionEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bokecc.sdk.mobile.live.eventbus.SubscriberExceptionEvent

  • public final class SubscriberExceptionEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    This Event is posted by CCEventBus when an exception occurs inside a subscriber's event handling method.
